<title>SOUTH KOREA: TABLE-Hotel Shilla H1 loss shrinks.</title>
<headline>TABLE-Hotel Shilla H1 loss shrinks.</headline>
<dateline>SEOUL 1997-08-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to June 30</p>
<p>	  (in billion won unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (won)			   loss  217  vs loss 237</p>
<p>    Net				   loss 3.91  vs loss 4.21</p>
<p>    Profit before tax		 loss 3.91  vs loss 4.20</p>
<p>    Revenue				  122.75  vs 114.51</p>
<p>NOTE - Hotel Shilla Co Ltd operates hotels in Seoul and Cheju and is involved in the duty free shopping and restaurant businesses. The figures were released by the Korea Listed Companies Association.</p>
